---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-24 border-t border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-10 text-sm text-slate-600">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Sthira <span class="font-normal text-slate-500">by SOS Markets</span></div>
        <p class="mt-2 max-w-md">
          Investing on autopilot — goal-based SIPs and pre-authorized rebalancing. Built
          for layman retail investors. The LLM explains. It does not trade.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs">
          A product by{' '}
          <a href="https://sosservices.online" class="hover:text-slate-900 underline-offset-4 hover:underline">
            SOS Services
          </a>
          .
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div>
          <div class="font-medium text-slate-900">Product</div>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li><a href="/#features" class="hover:text-slate-900">How it works</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-slate-900">Join waitlist</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-medium text-slate-900">Company</div>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-slate-900">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://sosservices.online" class="hover:text-slate-900">SOS Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-slate-900">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-medium text-slate-900">Legal</div>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li><a href="/legal/terms" class="hover:text-slate-900">Terms of Use</a></li>
            <li><a href="/legal/privacy" class="hover:text-slate-900">Privacy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/legal/risk" class="hover:text-slate-900">Risk disclosure</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 border-t border-slate-200 pt-6 text-xs">
      © {year} SOS Services. Sthira is in closed pilot — pending SEBI advisor onboarding.
      Investments in securities are subject to market risks; read all related documents
      carefully before investing.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
